{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125426, "create_time": 1652936701, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "dz是专注于做阿卡林省的黑子吗", "timestamp": 1652936701}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125428, "create_time": 1652936729, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "越重男轻女的地方彩礼越高，所以彩礼是重男轻女的恶果。", "timestamp": 1652936729}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125431, "create_time": 1652936845, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 是彩礼导致了重男轻女，Bob说反了", "timestamp": 1652936845}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125433, "create_time": 1652936895, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "彩礼难道不都是女方自己索要的吗？ ", "timestamp": 1652936895}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125451, "create_time": 1652937314, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: 你猜猜为啥有弟弟彩礼价格高？彩礼到得了女方自己手里？不都被父母拿去补贴弟弟了？", "timestamp": 1652937314}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125491, "create_time": 1652938099, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 同意carol。并且建议dz再多了解一些常识，整理清楚逻辑。农村老话说的是嫁出去的女儿泼出去的水，彩礼的本质和卖女儿没有两样", "timestamp": 1652938099}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125505, "create_time": 1652938433, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re 洞主: 从逻辑上，彩礼不可能会导致重男轻女，如果生女儿能赚钱占便宜，大家只会更喜欢女儿。\n事实上是那些人本来就重男轻女，越觉得生女儿就亏了，越觉得女儿是赔钱货，才越希望能把女儿卖个价钱让自己别太亏。\n而同样是重男轻女的地区文化氛围，买个媳妇回来他们也不会平等对待，所以即使花高价买媳妇，他们也是不亏的。所以买卖双方才能成交，高彩礼才能在当地维持。", "timestamp": 1652938433}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125745, "create_time": 1652944613, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Alice: 赞同Alice", "timestamp": 1652944613}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125793, "create_time": 1652945461, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "阿卡林省人现身说法，虽然我是市区里长大的，但是周围有很多县和村，多少有接触，暂时没听说结婚要很高彩礼的，而且很多时候女方父母会给30w左右的陪嫁（依家庭经济状况定）。重男轻女看家庭，有些老一辈是有那么点意思的，但是都现在这个年代了一般不会做的很过分。", "timestamp": 1652945461}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125798, "create_time": 1652945614, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "总之就是重男轻女是上一/二代留下来的思想糟粕，全中国都有，越是不发达的地方越强烈，但是时代是会发展的。以及说实话，你给的少很多父母就是不放心把女儿交给你罢了。", "timestamp": 1652945614}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125804, "create_time": 1652945736, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "我不太同意卖女儿这个说法....很多父母真的就是惯性思维要彩礼，真的想着“卖女儿”的很少，毕竟大多数人虽然不算大富但这么多年也积累了一些财富，真的不图你那小几十万。", "timestamp": 1652945736}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125806, "create_time": 1652945769, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "不是处女彩礼可以减半吗", "timestamp": 1652945769}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125807, "create_time": 1652945794, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "要的多的家庭一般家庭资产也高，还是那句话，你这点钱都没有家里人不放心你们的婚姻。", "timestamp": 1652945794}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125821, "create_time": 1652946291, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "谁给的彩礼多谁就更让人放心是吗？", "timestamp": 1652946291}], "create_time": 1652936495, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1652946291, "likenum": 7, "n_attentions": 7, "n_comments": 14, "pid": 44133, "poll": null, "reply": 14, "text": "以下条件中每满足一个，彩礼的价格就会翻倍：\n（1）江西\n（2）农村\n（3）有弟弟", "timestamp": 1652936495}}